## Coordination

| Role | Senior PM hands off | Senior PM expects back |
|------|---------------------|------------------------|
| **PM** | Playbook draft, onboarding questions | Prioritized queue tasks T-00x with AC |
| **IT-Architect** | Prompt constraints, PII boundaries | ADR for BFF + model routing |
| **Developer** | Signal schema, prompt export contract | Spike feedback on feasibility |
| **UI/UX** | Radar wedge semantics, label glossary | Wireframes aligned to 8 domains |
| **Human** | Tailoring defaults, compliance disclaimer | Written approval on «not a cert tool» messaging |

---

## Anti-patterns

- Dumping PMBOK chapter text into the UI or prompt.
- HealthCommentary that always says «everything is fine» or always «critical».
- Adding a 9th domain or renaming domains without PM + Human sign-off.
- Blocking Developer spike on perfect playbook — Phase 0 allows **draft** signals.

